      "cookedHtml": "<p><strong>We’re excited to roll out one of our most requested and most powerful features ever — and it’s something no other document app on <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> can do. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/collision.png?v=15\" title=\":collision:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":collision:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/file_folder.png?v=15\" title=\":file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Multi-Template Support (Inside One Board!)</strong></p>\n<p>You can now add multiple templates inside a single board view, each mapped to its own output column.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Upload as many templates as you need<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Keep everything in one clean, unified place<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Generate multiple files (PDF or DOCX) from a single item<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/right_arrow.png?v=15\" title=\":right_arrow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":right_arrow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> All with one click <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/high_voltage.png?v=15\" title=\":high_voltage:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":high_voltage:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=15\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Why This Is Game-Changing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>No switching views</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>No rebuilding setups</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>No complicated configurations</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Just a fast, clean, smart document workflow</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>This upgrade transforms DocCreate into a complete multi-document automation hub inside <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/fire.png?v=15\" title=\":fire:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":fire:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/blue_book.png?v=15\" title=\":blue_book:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blue_book:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Quick Links</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Install DocCreate : <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=5a10b399e0bf62c3b316ba5d004b56a7&amp;response_type=install\" title=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=5a10b399e0bf62c3b316ba5d004b56a7&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=5a10b399e0bf62c3b316ba5d004b56a7&amp;response_type=install</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Full feature details: <a href=\"https://doccreate.io/new-features/\" title=\"https://doccreate.io/new-features/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://doccreate.io/new-features/</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Full feature detail Document :<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DenXUDzLMIaeOkGz82quOfLkghg7F83a/view?usp=sharing\" title=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DenXUDzLMIaeOkGz82quOfLkghg7F83a/view?usp=sharing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DenXUDzLMIaeOkGz82quOfLkghg7F83a/view?usp=sharing</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Setup guide video: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/WbwHCx8Dee4?si=TsyemIhbrdBMn0Zc\" title=\"https://youtu.be/WbwHCx8Dee4?si=TsyemIhbrdBMn0Zc\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://youtu.be/WbwHCx8Dee4?si=TsyemIhbrdBMn0Zc</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />DocCreate Website : <a href=\"https://www.doccreate.io/\" title=\"https://www.doccreate.io\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://www.doccreate.io</a></p>"
